extendedInfo.description: Key Features:Calculates 9 p-Values  + 5 inverse probability values:1. Chi-Square test & inverse2. Correlation Coefficient3. Fisher F-test & inverse4. Fisher's Exact Test5. Normal Curve - Cumulative, 1-Tailed, 2-Tailed and inverse6. Significance of Mediation7. Student's t-TestDisplay graphs.

reviews.comment: Quality app. Very useful. But u should go for the probability app as it includes pvalue\'s, pdf\'s and cdf\'s. Goodwork!
